<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77c051c6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460k–4"><num value="460k–4">§ 460k–4.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated such funds as may be necessary to carry out the purposes of this subchapter, including the construction and maintenance of public recreational facilities.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77c051c7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/714/s5">Pub. L. 87–714, § 5</ref>, <date date="1962-09-28">Sept. 28, 1962</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/76/654">76 Stat. 654</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
